<h1>Draft - Summary - use of initials in Forenames</h1>

<p class="lead">This page considers the “problems” encountered when searching the GRO index, of which FreeBMD is an online version, due to the GRO's apparent changes in policy over time of how the index records and truncates the Forenames of individual entries using a mixture of the full forenames and initials. Advice is give how to minimise these problems when searching the Indexes.</p>
  

